Dialogue: 0,00:00:01.30,00:00:05.31,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ 自分らしさを力に
Dialogue: 0,00:00:05.31,00:00:08.82,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ 迷いながらでもいい
Dialogue: 0,00:00:08.82,00:00:13.83,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ 歩き出して
Dialogue: 0,00:00:13.83,00:00:15.83,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ もう一回
Dialogue: 0,00:00:15.83,00:00:18.84,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:00:18.84,00:00:22.34,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ 誰かの期待にずっと応え
Dialogue: 0,00:00:22.34,00:00:26.35,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ 誉められるのが好きなのですか
Dialogue: 0,00:00:26.35,00:00:29.86,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ なりたい自分を摺り替えても
Dialogue: 0,00:00:29.86,00:00:33.37,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ 笑顔はいつでも素敵ですか
Dialogue: 0,00:00:33.37,00:00:37.37,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ 始まりだけ
Dialogue: 0,00:00:37.37,00:00:40.88,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ 夢見て起きる
Dialogue: 0,00:00:40.88,00:00:44.89,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ その先なら
Dialogue: 0,00:00:44.89,00:00:50.40,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ いつか自分の腕で
Dialogue: 0,00:00:50.40,00:00:54.41,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ そうだ 大事な物は いつも
Dialogue: 0,00:00:54.41,00:00:58.35,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ 形のないものだけ
Dialogue: 0,00:00:58.35,00:01:02.36,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ 手に入れても なくしても
Dialogue: 0,00:01:02.36,00:01:05.36,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ 気付かぬまま
Dialogue: 0,00:01:05.36,00:01:09.87,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ そうさ 悲しみをやさしさに
Dialogue: 0,00:01:09.87,00:01:13.88,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ 自分らしさを力に
Dialogue: 0,00:01:13.88,00:01:17.39,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ 迷いながらでもいい
Dialogue: 0,00:01:17.39,00:01:22.40,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ 歩き出して
Dialogue: 0,00:01:22.40,00:01:24.90,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ もう一回
Dialogue: 0,00:01:31.87,00:01:35.38,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(我愛羅)う～あ～！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.95,0:01:45.95,Cart_A_Tre,,0,0,0,,El asesino a la luz de la luna
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.95,0:01:43.95,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,El asesino a la luz de la luna.
Dialogue: 0,00:01:45.90,00:01:54.35,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:01:54.35,00:01:57.36,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ﾅﾙﾄ)《こ… こいつ…》
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.23,0:01:57.41,Gen_Italics,,0,0,0,,Este tipo…
Dialogue: 0,00:01:57.36,00:02:00.36,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(我愛羅)うぅ…｡
Dialogue: 0,00:02:02.37,00:02:05.37,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｻｸﾗ)サスケ君！(ｻｽｹ)うっ…！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.81,0:02:04.01,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,¡Sasuke-kun!
Dialogue: 0,00:02:05.37,00:02:07.88,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ﾊﾟｯｸﾝ)《一足 遅かったか》
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.11,0:02:08.51,Gen_Italics,,0,0,0,,Llegamos tarde.
Dialogue: 0,00:02:11.38,00:02:13.39,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ﾃﾏﾘ)あいつら…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.11,0:02:13.65,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Son ellos.
Dialogue: 0,00:02:13.39,00:02:21.91,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:02:21.91,00:02:24.41,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,サ… サクラちゃん…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.32,0:02:24.73,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Sakura-chan…
Dialogue: 0,00:02:26.92,00:02:29.92,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,うっ… お前ら…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.70,0:02:30.06,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,¿Qué hacen aquí?
Dialogue: 0,00:02:29.92,00:02:31.93,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,《あっ これは…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.46,0:02:34.47,Gen_Italics,,0,0,0,,Eso es… Seguro que peleó sin cuidado.
Dialogue: 0,00:02:31.93,00:02:35.43,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,きっと むちゃな戦い方を…｡
Dialogue: 0,00:02:35.43,00:02:37.44,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,あの時みたいに…》
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.67,0:02:37.27,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Igual que esa vez.
Dialogue: 0,00:02:37.44,00:02:40.44,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,うあ～！ あ～！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.24,0:02:41.84,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,¡Sasuke-kun!
Dialogue: 0,00:02:40.44,00:02:42.95,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,サスケ君！《カカシ先生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.24,0:02:45.85,Gen_Italics,,0,0,0,,Pero Kakashi-sensei\Ndijo que no tenía de qué preocuparme.
Dialogue: 0,00:02:42.95,00:02:45.45,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,アザのこと心配ないって言ってたのに》
Dialogue: 0,00:02:45.45,00:02:48.46,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,誰だってばよ？ サクラちゃん｡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.85,0:02:48.35,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,¿Quién es, Sakura-chan?
Dialogue: 0,00:02:48.46,00:02:52.40,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,サクラちゃん！何よ もう！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.15,0:02:50.35,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,¡Sakura-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.75,0:02:51.95,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,¿Qué rayos quieres?
Dialogue: 0,00:02:52.40,00:02:56.41,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,こいつ 誰だってばよ!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.15,0:02:55.82,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,¿Quién es ese?
Dialogue: 0,00:02:56.41,00:02:59.92,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ﾊﾟｯｸﾝ)姿 形は変わっとるが
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.63,0:02:59.43,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Aunque tenga un aspecto distinto,
Dialogue: 0,00:02:59.92,00:03:02.42,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,我愛羅とかいうヤツじゃ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.55,0:03:02.56,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,se trata de Gaara.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:03.92,00:03:08.43,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜俺は母と呼ぶべき女の命を奪い生まれ落ちた｡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.25,0:03:08.43,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Nací arrebatándole la vida a la mujer\Na la que debería llamar madre.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:08.43,00:03:10.94,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,最強の忍となるべく
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.15,0:03:11.43,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Para que fuera el shinobi más fuerte,
Dialogue: 0,00:03:10.94,00:03:13.94,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,父親の忍術で 砂の化身を
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.43,0:03:16.78,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,mi padre usó ninjutsu para que\Nme poseyera el espíritu de la arena.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:13.94,00:03:16.95,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,この身に取りつかせてな｡
Dialogue: 0,00:03:16.95,00:03:20.96,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,俺は生まれながらの化け物だ＞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.18,0:03:20.38,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Nací siendo un monstruo.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:20.96,00:03:23.96,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,《こいつが それだってのか？》
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.51,0:03:24.33,Gen_Italics,,0,0,0,,¿A esto se refería?
Dialogue: 0,00:03:23.96,00:03:26.97,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,《あいつが サスケ君を…》
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.33,0:03:27.12,Gen_Italics,,0,0,0,,¿Fue él quien peleó contra Sasuke-kun?
Dialogue: 0,00:03:26.97,00:03:28.97,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ﾊﾟｯｸﾝ)おい 小娘｡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.12,0:03:28.95,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Muchacha.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:28.97,00:03:32.48,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,拙者は戦闘タイプじゃねえからあしからず｡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.33,0:03:32.42,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Yo no me especializo en combate,\Ntenlo en cuenta.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:32.48,00:03:34.48,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,そんなの見たら分かるわよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.82,0:03:34.83,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,¡Se ve a simple vista!
Dialogue: 0,00:03:34.48,00:03:36.49,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,うわっ！ あぁ！
Dialogue: 0,00:03:36.49,00:03:38.99,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,《とにかく ここから逃げて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.83,0:03:42.67,Gen_Italics,,0,0,0,,Tenemos que irnos de aquí y llevar\Na Sasuke-kun con Kakashi-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:38.99,00:03:42.50,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,サスケ君を何とかｶｶｼ先生の所へ連れてかなくちゃ》
Dialogue: 0,00:03:42.50,00:03:45.01,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(我愛羅)ハァ…｡
Dialogue: 0,00:03:45.01,00:03:47.01,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,お前…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.47,0:03:46.64,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Tú…
Dialogue: 0,00:03:48.51,00:03:50.52,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,うぅ！サスケ君！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.47,0:03:51.07,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,¡Sasuke-kun!
Dialogue: 0,00:03:50.52,00:03:54.46,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｶｶｼ)＜まっ お前の限界は２発｡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.07,0:03:56.58,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Tu límite son dos golpes.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:54.46,00:03:56.96,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,こんなところだ｡
Dialogue: 0,00:03:56.96,00:03:59.47,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,３発目は発動しない｡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.98,0:03:59.78,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,La tercera vez no se activará.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:59.47,00:04:02.47,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,よく覚えとけ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.18,0:04:01.39,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Recuérdalo.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:02.47,00:04:05.48,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,無理に術を発動しようとすれば
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.39,0:04:05.67,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Si intentas activarla por la fuerza,
Dialogue: 0,00:04:05.48,00:04:09.99,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,術は うまく発動しないうえにチャクラはゼロになり
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.67,0:04:09.93,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,no funcionará debidamente\Ny te quedarás sin chakra.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:09.99,00:04:13.49,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,下手したら死ぬぞ＞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.73,0:04:13.40,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,En el peor de los casos, morirás.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:19.01,00:04:21.51,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｶｶｼ)＜たとえ生き残ったとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.37,0:04:25.28,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Y aunque sobrevivas,\Nno te aportará nada bueno.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:21.51,00:04:26.02,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,お前にとって 決してろくなことにはならないよ｡
Dialogue: 0,00:04:26.02,00:04:29.03,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,特に お前はな＞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.48,0:04:28.48,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,A ti en especial.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:29.03,00:04:31.03,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜呪印か？＞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.27,0:04:30.75,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,¿Por el sello maldito?
Dialogue: 0,00:04:35.54,00:04:40.05,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｶｶｼ)＜憎しみに任せ呪印の力に依存すれば
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.09,0:04:40.15,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Si te dejas llevar por el odio\Ny dependes del sello,
Dialogue: 0,00:04:40.05,00:04:44.06,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,お前の成長は そこで止まる｡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.49,0:04:43.29,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,tu crecimiento terminará\Nen ese mismo instante.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:44.06,00:04:47.06,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,それじゃ お前はイタチに勝てないよ＞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.09,0:04:47.56,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Lo que significa\Nque no podrás vencer a Itachi.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:47.06,00:04:49.07,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,うっ！ あぁ！
Dialogue: 0,00:04:49.07,00:04:53.51,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,《とにかくこいつを抑え込まねえと！》
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.57,0:04:52.77,Gen_Italics,,0,0,0,,Tengo que reprimirlo.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:53.51,00:04:56.01,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,がはっ！サスケ君！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.54,0:04:55.74,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,¡Sasuke-kun!
Dialogue: 0,00:04:56.01,00:04:59.52,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(我愛羅)そうか お前は
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.54,0:04:58.94,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Tú eres…
Dialogue: 0,00:04:59.52,00:05:02.52,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,あの時 殺し損ねた…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.91,0:05:02.48,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,al que no pude matar aquella vez.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:04.03,00:05:08.54,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(我愛羅)＜自分のためだけに戦い自分だけを愛して生きる｡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.07,0:05:08.49,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Peleo solo por mí\Ny me amo únicamente a mí.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.49,0:05:12.09,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Mientras siga habiendo\Nextraños a los que matar,
Dialogue: 0,00:05:08.54,00:05:11.54,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,殺すべき他者が存在し続けるかぎり
Dialogue: 0,00:05:11.54,00:05:14.55,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,俺の存在は消えない＞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.09,0:05:14.46,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,mi existencia no terminará.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:16.05,00:05:17.56,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,に…
Dialogue: 0,00:05:17.56,00:05:20.06,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,逃げっぞ！ みんな！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.06,0:05:20.16,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,¡Nos vamos, chicos!
Dialogue: 0,00:05:20.06,00:05:30.07,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:05:33.09,00:05:35.59,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(我愛羅)死ね うちはサスケ～！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.11,0:05:35.58,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,¡Muere, Sasuke Uchiha!
Dialogue: 0,00:05:37.60,00:05:39.60,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(我愛羅)うっ！
Dialogue: 0,00:05:39.60,00:05:41.60,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,サクラちゃん！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.98,0:05:40.98,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,¡Sakura-chan!
Dialogue: 0,00:05:52.56,00:05:54.56,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,どけ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.76,0:05:53.73,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,¡Apártate!
Dialogue: 0,00:05:56.07,00:05:58.07,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,うあっ！
Dialogue: 0,00:06:06.09,00:06:08.09,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,うぅ！
Dialogue: 0,00:06:10.10,00:06:12.10,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,サクラちゃん！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.54,0:06:11.81,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,¡Sakura-chan!
Dialogue: 0,00:06:15.11,00:06:18.61,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,あの我愛羅の前に立ちはだかるなんて｡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.18,0:06:18.38,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,No puedo creer\Nque se pusiera delante de Gaara.
Dialogue: 0,00:06:18.61,00:06:21.12,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,くそ！ くそ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.75,0:06:24.22,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Maldición, ¿qué puedo hacer?
Dialogue: 0,00:06:21.12,00:06:25.13,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,どうすりゃいいんだってばよ一体｡
Dialogue: 0,00:06:25.13,00:06:27.63,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,うぅ…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.59,0:06:29.59,Gen_Italics,,0,0,0,,No puedo hacerle frente.
Dialogue: 0,00:06:27.63,00:06:30.14,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,《こいつとだけは…》
Dialogue: 0,00:06:30.14,00:06:33.64,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(我愛羅)＜さぁ 感じさせてくれ＞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.19,0:06:32.80,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Hagan que me sienta vivo.
Dialogue: 0,00:06:33.64,00:06:36.64,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,うぅ！ うぅ…｡
Dialogue: 0,00:06:40.16,00:06:43.66,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,うっ！ なぜ…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.11,0:06:43.21,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,¿Por qué?
Dialogue: 0,00:06:43.66,00:06:51.11,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:06:51.11,00:06:53.61,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(夜叉丸)＜我愛羅様落ち着いてください！＞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.15,0:06:53.32,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Cálmese, Gaara-sama.
Dialogue: 0,00:06:53.61,00:06:55.62,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(我愛羅)うっ うぅ！
Dialogue: 0,00:07:09.15,00:07:11.15,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜やっぱりダメだ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.37,0:07:10.97,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,No puedo.
Dialogue: 0,00:07:11.15,00:07:14.66,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,砂が邪魔する＞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.77,0:07:13.77,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,La arena se interpone.
Dialogue: 0,00:07:14.66,00:07:16.66,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(夜叉丸)＜我愛羅様＞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.93,0:07:15.87,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Gaara-sama.
Dialogue: 0,00:07:16.66,00:07:19.17,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(我愛羅)＜夜叉丸＞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.23,0:07:18.91,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Yashamaru.
Dialogue: 0,00:07:19.17,00:07:23.17,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜こう見えても医療班としてあなたの体調を管理し
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.59,0:07:21.55,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Como parte del equipo médico,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.55,0:07:26.89,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,debo cuidar su salud y protegerlo\Npor orden del Kazekage-sama.
Dialogue: 0,00:07:23.17,00:07:27.18,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,常にお守りするよう 風影様から仰せつかっている身です｡
Dialogue: 0,00:07:27.18,00:07:30.69,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,私の前でそんなまねは やめてください＞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.28,0:07:30.35,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,No haga algo así frente a mí, por favor.
Dialogue: 0,00:07:32.69,00:07:36.20,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜とはいっても砂が守ってくれますか＞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.72,0:07:36.06,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Aunque ya lo protege la arena.
Dialogue: 0,00:07:39.21,00:07:41.71,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜夜叉丸 ごめん＞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.26,0:07:41.80,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Lo siento, Yashamaru.
Dialogue: 0,00:07:41.71,00:07:45.22,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜え？ あぁ これ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.20,0:07:47.04,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,No son más que rasguños.
Dialogue: 0,00:07:45.22,00:07:47.22,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,ただのかすり傷です＞
Dialogue: 0,00:07:49.23,00:07:53.23,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜傷って 痛い？＞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.44,0:07:53.01,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,¿Las heridas duelen?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.03,0:07:58.98,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Un poco, pero se curan enseguida.
Dialogue: 0,00:07:55.17,00:07:59.18,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜まぁ 少しはでも すぐ治りますよ＞
Dialogue: 0,00:08:07.20,00:08:10.70,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(我愛羅)＜ねぇ 夜叉丸＞(夜叉丸)＜何です？＞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.22,0:08:08.83,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Yashamaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.83,0:08:09.89,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,¿Sí?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.69,0:08:12.36,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,¿Cómo es el dolor?
Dialogue: 0,00:08:10.70,00:08:13.21,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(我愛羅)＜痛いって何なの？＞
Dialogue: 0,00:08:15.71,00:08:19.72,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜僕 一度も傷 出来たことないから
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.83,0:08:22.25,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Nunca he tenido una herida,\Nasí que no sé lo que se siente.
Dialogue: 0,00:08:19.72,00:08:23.23,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,どんな感じかなぁって＞
Dialogue: 0,00:08:23.23,00:08:25.23,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜う～ん…｡
Dialogue: 0,00:08:25.23,00:08:28.24,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,どう言ったらいいのかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.57,0:08:27.98,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,No sé cómo explicárselo.
Dialogue: 0,00:08:28.24,00:08:32.25,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,苦しいっていうかつらいっていうか｡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.38,0:08:31.75,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Es duro de soportar y te hace sufrir.
Dialogue: 0,00:08:32.25,00:08:35.25,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,つまり 打たれたり 切られたり
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.55,0:08:35.37,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Como cuando te golpean\No te hacen un corte.
Dialogue: 0,00:08:35.25,00:08:37.76,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,我慢できない状態で
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.75,0:08:41.72,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Es una situación anómala en la que\Nno puedes aguantar como siempre.
Dialogue: 0,00:08:37.76,00:08:42.27,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,普通にいられない感覚って言ったらいいのかな？
Dialogue: 0,00:08:42.27,00:08:44.27,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,アハ… うまく言えないですが
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.52,0:08:47.89,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,No sé explicarlo bien,\Npero no es bueno.
Dialogue: 0,00:08:44.27,00:08:47.78,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,あまり よい状態ではないということですかね＞
Dialogue: 0,00:08:47.78,00:08:57.79,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:08:59.73,00:09:03.24,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜夜叉丸＞(夜叉丸)＜はい＞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.01,0:09:01.08,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Yashamaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.49,0:09:02.55,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,¿Sí?
Dialogue: 0,00:09:03.24,00:09:07.75,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜じゃあ 夜叉丸は 僕のこと
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.34,0:09:09.52,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Entonces, ¿me odias?
Dialogue: 0,00:09:07.75,00:09:10.25,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,嫌い？＞
Dialogue: 0,00:09:10.25,00:09:20.26,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.53,0:09:25.73,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,En la vida, la gente lastima\Na otros y es lastimada.
Dialogue: 0,00:09:20.78,00:09:23.78,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(夜叉丸)＜人は傷つけたり傷つけられたりして
Dialogue: 0,00:09:23.78,00:09:27.79,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,生きていくものですでも 人は そう簡単には
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.73,0:09:29.50,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Pero no se odia tan fácilmente.
Dialogue: 0,00:09:27.79,00:09:30.29,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,嫌いになれないものですよ＞
Dialogue: 0,00:09:32.30,00:09:35.30,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜ありがとう 夜叉丸｡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.37,0:09:35.17,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Gracias, Yashamaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.17,0:09:38.78,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Entiendo un poco mejor\Nlo que es el dolor.
Dialogue: 0,00:09:35.30,00:09:38.81,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,痛いっていうのが何となく分かった気がする＞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.78,0:09:39.95,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Ya veo.
Dialogue: 0,00:09:38.81,00:09:41.82,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(夜叉丸)＜そうですか ん？＞
Dialogue: 0,00:09:41.82,00:09:45.83,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(我愛羅)＜じゃあ僕もケガしてるのかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.35,0:09:47.31,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Puede ser que yo también\N me haya lastimado.
Dialogue: 0,00:09:45.83,00:09:48.33,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,みんなと同じで｡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.12,0:09:50.66,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Siempre me duele.
Dialogue: 0,00:09:48.33,00:09:51.34,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,いつも 痛いんだ｡
Dialogue: 0,00:09:51.34,00:09:53.84,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,血は出てないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.46,0:09:53.46,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,No sale sangre,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.46,0:09:56.63,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,pero me duele mucho el pecho.
Dialogue: 0,00:09:53.84,00:09:56.85,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,ここんとこが すごく痛いんだ＞
Dialogue: 0,00:10:10.37,00:10:12.38,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜あっ！＞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.55,0:10:23.76,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Las heridas del cuerpo\Nparecen dolorosas porque sangran,
Dialogue: 0,00:10:18.89,00:10:23.90,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜体の傷は 確かに血が流れて痛そうに見えるかもしれません｡
Dialogue: 0,00:10:23.90,00:10:27.41,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,でも 時がたてば自然と痛みは消え
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.15,0:10:27.29,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,pero con el tiempo, el dolor desaparece.
Dialogue: 0,00:10:27.41,00:10:31.42,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,薬を使えば さらに治りは早い｡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.69,0:10:30.49,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Y más si usas medicina.
Dialogue: 0,00:10:31.42,00:10:34.92,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,しかし やっかいなのは心の傷です｡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.66,0:10:34.87,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Las más problemáticas\Nson las heridas del corazón.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.87,0:10:37.23,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Son las más difíciles de curar.
Dialogue: 0,00:10:34.92,00:10:37.93,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,治りにくいこと このうえない＞
Dialogue: 0,00:10:37.93,00:10:39.93,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜心の傷？＞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.04,0:10:40.04,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,¿Las heridas del corazón?
Dialogue: 0,00:10:39.93,00:10:43.94,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(夜叉丸)＜体の傷と 心の傷は少し違います｡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.04,0:10:43.53,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Hay una ligera diferencia entre las dos.
Dialogue: 0,00:10:43.94,00:10:47.45,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,体の傷と違って塗り薬もなければ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.97,0:10:47.73,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,A diferencia de las del cuerpo,\Nno hay medicina para las del corazón,
Dialogue: 0,00:10:47.45,00:10:50.45,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,一生 治らないことだってあります＞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.73,0:10:50.01,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,y a veces no se curan nunca.
Dialogue: 0,00:10:50.45,00:10:56.90,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.79,0:11:00.79,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Pero hay una cosa\Nque sí sana las heridas del corazón.
Dialogue: 0,00:10:56.90,00:10:58.91,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(夜叉丸)＜でも ただ一つだけ
Dialogue: 0,00:10:58.91,00:11:02.41,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,心の傷を癒やせるものがあります｡
Dialogue: 0,00:11:02.41,00:11:04.92,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,ただ これは やっかいな薬で
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.53,0:11:07.73,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,No obstante, es una medicina\Nque solo se puede recibir de otros.
Dialogue: 0,00:11:04.92,00:11:07.92,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,他人からしかもらうことはできません＞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.73,0:11:10.53,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,¿Y qué debo hacer para conseguirla?
Dialogue: 0,00:11:07.92,00:11:10.93,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜何？ どうすれば僕は…＞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.93,0:11:14.87,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Lo que sana las heridas del corazón es…
Dialogue: 0,00:11:10.93,00:11:13.94,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜心の傷を癒やせるもの
Dialogue: 0,00:11:13.94,00:11:15.94,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,それは…＞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.84,0:11:19.44,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,el amor.
Dialogue: 0,00:11:17.94,00:11:21.45,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜愛情です＞(我愛羅)＜愛情？＞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.89,0:11:21.44,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,¿El amor?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.44,0:11:22.41,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Sí.
Dialogue: 0,00:11:21.45,00:11:22.95,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜はい＞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.81,0:11:25.01,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,¿Y cómo se consigue?
Dialogue: 0,00:11:22.95,00:11:24.96,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜ど… どうしたらもらえるの？
Dialogue: 0,00:11:24.96,00:11:27.96,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,僕は 何をすれば この痛みを…＞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.01,0:11:27.38,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,¿Qué debo hacer para aliviar el dolor?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.79,0:11:31.39,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Usted ya recibe esa medicina.
Dialogue: 0,00:11:27.96,00:11:31.47,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜我愛羅様はもう すでにもらっていますよ＞
Dialogue: 0,00:11:31.47,00:11:33.47,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(我愛羅)＜え？＞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.45,0:11:41.17,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,El amor procede\Nde la gente cercana a usted
Dialogue: 0,00:11:36.48,00:11:38.99,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(夜叉丸)＜愛情は 自分の身近にいる
Dialogue: 0,00:11:38.99,00:11:41.49,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,大切な人に尽くしてあげたいと
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.17,0:11:44.17,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,que quiere ayudarlo y protegerlo.
Dialogue: 0,00:11:41.49,00:11:44.50,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,慈しみ 見守る心｡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.17,0:11:45.83,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Como mi hermana.
Dialogue: 0,00:11:44.50,00:11:46.50,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,姉さんのようにね｡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.23,0:11:50.31,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Creo que ella siempre lo amó.
Dialogue: 0,00:11:46.50,00:11:51.01,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,姉さんは 我愛羅様をずっと愛していたのだと思います｡
Dialogue: 0,00:11:51.01,00:11:56.45,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,砂の守鶴は 本来攻撃のための生き霊です｡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.51,0:11:55.81,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Shukaku de la Arena\Nes un espíritu ofensivo.
Dialogue: 0,00:11:56.45,00:11:59.96,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,砂が自動的に我愛羅様を守ろうとするのは
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.61,0:11:59.81,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Que la arena\Nlo proteja incondicionalmente
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.81,0:12:01.78,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,se debe al amor de su madre.
Dialogue: 0,00:11:59.96,00:12:02.97,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,母親としての愛情｡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.58,0:12:07.52,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Creo que la arena\Nencierra la voluntad de su madre.
Dialogue: 0,00:12:02.97,00:12:04.97,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,あの砂の中には
Dialogue: 0,00:12:04.97,00:12:08.48,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,母親の意志が込められているんだと思います｡
Dialogue: 0,00:12:08.48,00:12:12.49,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,姉さん 死んでもなお
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.03,0:12:15.13,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Seguro que mi hermana\Nquería protegerlo incluso tras morir.
Dialogue: 0,00:12:12.49,00:12:15.49,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,我愛羅様を守りたかったんだろうな＞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.90,0:12:19.11,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Yashamaru.
Dialogue: 0,00:12:18.00,00:12:22.00,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜夜叉丸＞(夜叉丸)＜何です？＞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.90,0:12:21.07,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,¿Qué sucede?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.87,0:12:26.04,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Gracias por detenerme antes.
Dialogue: 0,00:12:22.00,00:12:24.51,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜さっきは ありがとう｡
Dialogue: 0,00:12:24.51,00:12:26.51,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,僕を止めてくれて＞
Dialogue: 0,00:12:26.51,00:12:29.02,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜どういたしまして｡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.84,0:12:28.45,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,No fue nada.
Dialogue: 0,00:12:29.02,00:12:31.02,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,我愛羅様は
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.24,0:12:34.01,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Usted es una persona\Nmuy importante para mí.
Dialogue: 0,00:12:31.02,00:12:34.53,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,私の身近にいる大切な人ですからね＞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.54,0:13:00.94,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,¿Comprende mi dolor?
Dialogue: 0,00:12:57.01,00:12:59.01,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(夜叉丸)＜分かりますか？
Dialogue: 0,00:12:59.01,00:13:01.51,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,私の痛みが…＞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.13,0:13:12.12,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Sabe a hierro.
Dialogue: 0,00:13:10.53,00:13:14.04,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(我愛羅)＜鉄の味がする＞
Dialogue: 0,00:13:14.04,00:13:17.05,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,うぅ～！
Dialogue: 0,00:13:17.05,00:13:19.55,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,ハァ ハァ…｡
Dialogue: 0,00:13:19.55,00:13:22.06,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,ぐっ…！
Dialogue: 0,00:13:22.06,00:13:24.56,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(我愛羅)ぐっ！ あぁ！
Dialogue: 0,00:13:24.56,00:13:28.57,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,うぅ！ う～！
Dialogue: 0,00:13:28.57,00:13:31.57,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,う～！ あぁ…｡
Dialogue: 0,00:13:33.61,00:13:43.62,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:13:46.07,00:13:48.57,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(猿飛)おっ…｡
Dialogue: 0,00:13:48.57,00:13:52.07,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(大蛇丸)うぅ… うっ…｡
Dialogue: 0,00:13:54.58,00:13:58.59,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(大蛇丸)うっ！ う… うぅ！
Dialogue: 0,00:14:04.60,00:14:07.61,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,うあ～…｡
Dialogue: 0,00:14:07.61,00:14:11.12,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,あ～‼
